Package com.saic.uicds.core.infrastructure.endpoint

The com.saic.uicds.core.endpoint package contains the Java classes that implement the UICDS Core Web Service Interface and therefore these Javadoc pages document the WSDL interfaces available for each of the UICDS core services.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AgreementServiceEndpoint The UICDS Agreement Service provides a means to define information sharing agreements between UICDS Cores.
DirectoryServiceEndpoint The Directory Service allows UICDS clients to retrieve information on common data sources, common tools, and services available on this core installation.
InterestGroupServiceEndpoint The Interest Group Service allows clients to manage UICDS Interest Group.
LoggingServiceEndpoint This service provides Apache log4j functionality to allow the client to log any type of information into the log file.
NotificationServiceEndpoint The UICDS system Notification Service provides a WS-Notification (WSN) compliant service interface to provide push and pull based notifications to UICDS Notification Consumers (UICDS clients).
ResourceInstanceServiceEndpoint The UICDS Resource Instance service provides a means to create, discover, update, and remove UICDS resource instances.
ResourceProfileServiceEndpoint The UICDS Resource Profile Management Service provides a means to create, discover, and update UICDS Resource Profiles.
